msgctxt "0001"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>The two bodies that had disappeared were right there.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0002"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>The smell of blood made me gag...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0003"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>What I saw <CLT><CLT 3>before my eyes<CLT><CLT 4> was unquestionable,\n"
"unavoidable, unwavering reality.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0004"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>And then...I heard the announcement for a second time.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0005"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>*Ding dong, ding dong*\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0006"
msgid "A body has been discovered!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0007"
msgid ""
"After a certain amount of time, which you may use\n"
"however you like, the <CLT 3>class trial<CLT> will begin!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0008"
msgid "And so here we are!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0009"
msgid ""
"Without further ado, let me give you all <CLT 3>the next\n"
"Monokuma File<CLT>!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0010"
msgid ""
"I was going to hand them out when you found the bodies\n"
"the first time, but I thought something might happen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0011"
msgid ""
"It was really hard to resist, but...turns out I was\n"
"right!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0012"
msgid "Just hand it over already."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0013"
msgid ""
"Now, make sure to investigate with all of your mental\n"
"might and prepare for the class trial!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0014"
msgid "Okay, see ya later!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0015"
msgid ""
"Well then, now that we've found the bodies, all that's\n"
"left is to uncover the culprit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0016"
msgid "H-Hold on..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0017"
msgid "How can you be so...so calm...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0018"
msgid "I mean, they're *dead*, ya know!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0019"
msgid "Dead! Gone forever! They're never coming back!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0020"
msgid "Awful... This is all just too awful!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0021"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Hina suddenly burst into tears.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0022"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>She clutched at Hifumi's lifeless body.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0023"
msgid "Wh-Who would do this...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0024"
msgid "Why...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0025"
msgid "WHYYY!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0026"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Large, wet tears fell from her eyes.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0027"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>The tears landed on Hifumi's cheeks.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0028"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>If this were some world of make-believe, that might\n"
"have been when Hifumi opened his eyes.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0029"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>But this wasn't a movie.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0030"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>This wasn't...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0031"
msgid "Ng..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0032"
msgid "He's alive again!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0033"
msgid "Where...am I?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0034"
msgid "Cold...so cold... Is...winter coming?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0035"
msgid "H-Hifumi! Wake up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0036"
msgid "...Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0037"
msgid "Ahh...that's right..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0038"
msgid "I remember now... Hope's Peak..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0039"
msgid "Come on! You gotta wake up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0040"
msgid "I remember...everything..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0041"
msgid "Before...I'd met you...all..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0042"
msgid "I'd met...you all..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0043"
msgid ""
"His memories are all blending together. He has nothing\n"
"useful to offer us..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0044"
msgid "Ahh...the light..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0045"
msgid "It's...reaching out...to me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0046"
msgid "Like...the tail...of a comet..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0047"
msgid "Hey, Hifumi! Who was it? Who attacked you!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0048"
msgid "Who tried to kill you!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0049"
msgid "Who...killed me...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0050"
msgid "That's right... I remember...their name..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0051"
msgid "Y...Yasu..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0052"
msgid "...hi...ro..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0053"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "0054"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>His eyes closed.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0055"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>And they never opened again.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0056"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Death for the second time...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0057"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Absolute, undeniable death...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0058"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>No matter how many more of Hina's tears splashed his\n"
"face...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0059"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>...there was no second miracle. Reality set in again.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0060"
msgid ""
"This isn't some stereotypical fantasy world. Tears\n"
"can't restore a person's vitality."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0061"
msgid ""
"You have no tears, do you? No blood in your veins, no\n"
"calcium in your bones. At least you have your meat..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0062"
msgid "You're just angry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0063"
msgid ""
"Going out of his way to return, just to leave us with\n"
"those unnecessary dying words."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0064"
msgid "Now this game has become exceedingly boring."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0065"
msgid "He said...Yasuhiro, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0066"
msgid "Yasuhiro Hagakure..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0067"
msgid ""
"That is the only person he could have been referring\n"
"to."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0068"
msgid "And with that, the case is solved."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0069"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Assaulting people, and even killing Taka and Hifumi...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0070"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>And then going so far as to hide their bodies...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0071"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>A criminal that hides his face behind a mask, and uses\n"
"a bunch of giant wooden hammers...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0072"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Is that what Hiro is...?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0073"
msgid ""
"If it's true, I can't forgive him... No way can I ever\n"
"forgive him!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0074"
msgid "To kill two of our friends...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0075"
msgid ""
"Anyway, it's about time we tracked down the culprit in\n"
"our little life-or-death game here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0076"
msgid ""
"Although...this time it's not all that life-or-death.\n"
"The trial will conclude without much trouble."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0077"
msgid "Yes, it does look that way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0078"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "0079"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>It's...going to begin again.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0080"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>We have to go through this...one more time.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0081"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0082"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I have to accept it...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0083"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I have no choice but to go through with this. To make\n"
"sure everyone survives...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0084"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>...I just have to do it!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
